Package DAO

Class DBCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • DAO.DBCache
  • public class DBCache
extends java.lang.Object
    Responsible for keeping the local cache of all the entries in the customer, appointment, user, firstleveldiv, country and contact tables. Implemented using Singleton to ensure only one instance of cache exists. Offers getters for all the hashmaps with entries per object and update methods for all the maps
    Author:
    Iulia Bejsovec
